### Generative Pre-trained Transformer 1 (GPT-1)

**[OpenAI](/OpenAI)** | **Initial release:** June 2018 (7 years ago) | **Repository:** [github.com/openai/finetune-transformer-lm](/github.com/openai/finetune-transformer-lm) | **Successor:** [GPT-2](/GPT-2) | **Type:** [Large language model](/Large_language_model), [Generative pre-trained transformer](/Generative_pre-trained_transformer) | **License:** [MIT](/MIT_license) | **Website:** openai.com/blog/language-unsupervised/

